&lt;p&gt;A properties file lookup would be ideal.  The problem is not so much with&lt;br/&gt;
digester itself.  It&apos;s with the numerous consumers of digester who accept the&lt;br/&gt;
default digester behavior and the inability to effect digester&apos;s choice of&lt;br/&gt;
classloader when digester is an indirect dependency.  An optional properties&lt;br/&gt;
file would definitely maintain the existing behavior yet allow sufficient&lt;br/&gt;
configurability when needed.  Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
